 she needed to worry about.<br>
"Hephaestus," she spoke his name softly, and awaited his atttention. <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uixhephaestusxi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>IX Hephaestus XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/18/02 12:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=204.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Many weeks later...</span><hr size=1> ::Hephaestus felt the presence of his mother behind him.  He decided to wait a few minutes and pound out the last of his current project before acknowledging her presence.  After putting his forge hammer down, he turned around to face her.  He smiled slightly to her, for no other reason than just to smile.  He folded his massive arms for a moment examining her, all he wore was that simple cloth wrapped around his waist.  That had become sort of his work uniform.  His body was glistening from the sweat and heat, but also quite dirty from the soot and ash that was prevelent in the air::<br>
<br>
&quot;How do you do this day Mother?&quot;<br>
<br>
::He put his infamous walking crutch underneath his arm and hobbled over to another work bench.  From it he pulled a golden colored belt, highly decorated belt.  Inlaid with finely sculptured and molded golden vines and jewels, the belt is one of the most ornate he has made to date for an amazon.::<br>
<br>
&quot;Is it to your satisfaction?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 197<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(1/24/02 12:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=204.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/qhera.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Many weeks later...</span><hr size=1> Hera watched him continue his work and then brought her lips to smile as he greeted her.  "I am well, son.  It seems Olympus is at peace for now...and as is the world of mortals..for the moment."<br>
Pale icy eyes watched as the God of forge, steel and heat brought for the shiny golden belt.  Hera was stark against her son, in her black dress and pale skin.  "It is most beautiful, son.  No one could do any work that could come close.  The new amazon queen shall be very proud." <br>
Hera stepped forward, "I thank you very much for your hard work and craftmanship." <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=204.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=204.topic&start=41&stop=46>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=204.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=204.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=204.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=204.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=204.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=204.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=204.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving